headline: Westchester, a Chubb Company, Appoints Alex Faynberg Head of Healthy Paws Pet Insurance
summary: Westchester, Chubb's Excess and Surplus Lines Division, today announced the appointment of Alex Faynberg, currently Division President of Chubb Workplace Benefits (CWB), to Executive Vice President and Head of Healthy Paws, a Chubb company, effective March 3, 2025.

headline: Davis Financial Fund 2025 Annual Review
summary: Since its inception in 1991, Davis Financial Fund has invested in durable, well-managed financial services companies at value prices, which the fund could hold for the long term.
